QuestData.Title: Idling Pie
QuestData.Description:
Now that we have the wares back we can finish up here. But all my workers are lazin' about the city.
Find where they're hidin' and 'encourage' 'em to head back here. A little leftover pie to the face, should have 'em runnin'.

Objectives.Objective: Worker Woken near the Orgrimmar Embassy
Worker Woken in the Valley of Strength
